The paper deals with safety verification of direct perception neural networks, which are used for autonomous vehicles. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and systems and control (cs.SY). Among these, machine learning and computer vision are the most likely categories, as the paper deals with neural networks that take camera images as inputs and produce high-level features. Artificial intelligence is also likely, as the paper deals with autonomous vehicles. Robotics and systems and control are less likely, but still possible, as the paper deals with control decisions for autonomous vehicles.
